Reports a misplaced <code>@import</code> statement.
<p>
  According to the <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@import">specification</a>,
  an <code>@import</code> rule must be defined at the top of the stylesheet, before any other at-rule
  (except <code>@charset</code> and <code>@layer</code>) and style declarations, or it will be ignored.
</p>
